Questions:
What will happen if you choose to withdraw from the LCI-HEM-BMT-IMPPACT-001 study?
A) You will be required to pay a penalty fee for early withdrawal;
B) Your relationship with the investigators or Atrium Health will be negatively affected;
C) You will not be able to receive any standard medical treatment in the future;
D) Your decision to withdraw will not affect your future relations with the investigators or Atrium Health.

Correct answer: D

If you experience any medical problems or suffer a research-related injury during the study, whom should you contact?

A) The Study Subject Adviser;
B) The Principal Investigator listed on the first page of the consent document;
C) A family member or friend;
D) Your personal physician not associated with the study.

Correct answer: B) The Principal Investigator listed on the first page of the consent document;
